OOC: What is WheelJack-X's location?


Battera::

She flew down, floating on a warm air current, she went searching for 
Wheeljack-X. She hoped she could find him and get word to him without 
blowing her cover. She couldn't risk a transmission at this point. 
She only hoped to be able to convince him that she was on thier side 
and her mission was valid. Also making suer he knew of her plan to 
get Nightlight back. If things went wrong, her life would be 
terninated.  She flew lower, trying to scan for the maximal 
signatures for Wheeljack-X.
